Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:01.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:05.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings\na group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:07.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:11.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the few remaining shards of the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:13.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:17.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demon Ninjas come after\nthe blade of the Naginata of Kenkon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:20.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I end up becoming separated\nfrom Inuyasha and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And thus, I begin a fierce struggle to\nsurvive along with Hojo's ancestor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My ancestor, Akitoki Hojo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:06.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who lived 500 years ago\nduring the feudal {\i1}age....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at his wife's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:08.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hojo's ancestor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:15.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What if...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:18.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't return to the modern age and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}ended up marrying\NHojo here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:29.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one after the blade is\nthe leader of the Demon Ninjas, Hoshiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:35.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Hoshiyomi is the one who\nmade Kaijinbo forge the Naginata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:43.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Akitoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:50.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:08.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have time for\nthe likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:19.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Genbu of the Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Byakko of the Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seiryu of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suzaku of the Flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see how you counter\nour Demon Ninja doppleganger technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why the hell are they circling us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango and I will handle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, go after Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:39.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're starting to annoy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be safe... Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:53.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Hoshiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:07.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're Hoshiyomi, huh?\NMove outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:11.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:13.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Ninja {\i1}technique....{\i0}\NShadow Incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To be saved by the Ken {\i1}blade....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such fortune in the midst of misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Kagome?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:39.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grab onto this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, we'll be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:05:00.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh! Misfortune has brought\nme even more fortune!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this mean the end\nof all my misfortune?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Hojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just another {\i1}misfortune....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:12.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I'm quite used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:17.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:19.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The river is ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:33.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop already. It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just who the hell is he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Hoshiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go after the Ken blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which is the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, this is such a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He seems quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll deal with Hoshiyomi.\NFind Kagome and Hojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, take us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:19.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hoshiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I once heard of a half-demon who\nfought Kaijinbo and his sword, Tokijin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His name was Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}Kaijinbo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I seem to remember a guy\nwith that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you protect\nthe Naginata of Kenkon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:44.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which was forged by Kaijinbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have no affinity for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I let the likes you possess\na demonic blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,nothing good will come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Ninja tricks don't\nwork on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:16.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:21.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sword trick you used\nto defeat Kaijinbo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,lives up to its reputation indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, I'll prove to {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:31.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that you are no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll blow you and your shadow\noutta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:41.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Ninja {\i1}technique....{\i0}\NShadow Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:41.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:46.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- What's going on?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body won't move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome and Hojo fell\nfrom this waterfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0} They probably were\nswept away by the rapids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If they fell from that distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there's no way\nthey could have survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't be so morbid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:16.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:28.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}Kagome's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, use your Fox Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....all{\i0} right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:39.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, I'm going to check\nthe bottom of the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are whirlpools in\nthe basin of these falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The aura of the Ken blade is\ncoming from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:13.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're giving me the creeps!\NStop acting like that, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aww. That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:16.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:18.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:20.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does your leg hurt, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to the medicinal herbs\nyou applied, the pain's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:42.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm such a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I carry the weight of\nthe Hojo name on my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're not that\nheavy in {\i1}comparison....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:55.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0} I didn't mean\nit quite like {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not heavy, {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:03.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just another slight {\i1}misfortune....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:13.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Sorry....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,J-Just another slight {\i1}misfortune....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no sign of\nbeing followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So let's stop here\nto rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:43.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope we can meet up\nwith Inuyasha and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if worse comes to worst,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we'll have to go to Furai Shrine\nby ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and seal the Ken blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm definitely not as\nstrong as {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:57.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But when the time comes\nto step up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, Akitoki, can be of service!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't do a thing\non an empty stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I'll go find something\nto eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Great! The contents of\nmy backpack weren't washed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:11.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not much, but here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so honored to be able to\neat food that you prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:21.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to compliment\nme on instant {\i1}noodles....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0} You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:29.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's delicious! Such a delicacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:35.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I think of the man who\ngets to eat your cooking every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous, I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:38.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}don't....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:40.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:50.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I know you're traveling\nwith a monk and a {\i1}half-demon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't say that they're\nsuitable for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:53.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But somewhere under\nthis {\i1}sky....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there exists a man who was\nborn to share his destiny with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Destiny, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, is there someone?\NAre you engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:12.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Especially since being the heir\nof the Hojo family is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,not without its {\i1}problems....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So many things are\nhappening in this era,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and it must be hard to\nfind a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, I'd jump at the chance\nto marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,F-Forget what I {\i1}said....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's rest a bit longer,\nthen we should head for Furai {\i1}Shrine....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:00.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,KAGOME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Why am I remembering that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:05.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only ones who can handle\na demon sword
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,are demons or half-demons\nlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's impossible for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:19.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's impossible for humans!\NYou guys don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's impossible for humans!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:28.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if there's a deep river\nbetween demons and humans...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that simply can't be crossed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could the "Kagome" that was\nwritten on that scroll be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:45.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! Those humans\nare defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's our chance to attack them\nand take the Ken blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:50.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you sense it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:55.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The aura emanating from\nthe blade is so strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:58.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we wouldn't be able to handle it,\nlet alone control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:02.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I'd be able to\ntaste blood again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll wait until\NMaster Hoshiyomi gets {\i1}here....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suzaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That picture you found {\i1}earlier....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:10.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} Maybe we can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:35.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the Kon blade.\NIsn't the aura magnificent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you have Kaijinbo\nmake such a blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you want\nthe other blade so badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While this blade means\neverything to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it has absolutely no value\nto you and your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you back off,\NI'll spare the other humans, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or....will you throw\naway your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:12.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:16.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does the power of the Shadow Hold\nfade as my shadow fades?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:21.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I ain't about to waste my life\nover a demon blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:24.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're smarter than I expected,\nhalf-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are a fool, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what the hell does\nthe Naginata of Kenkon mean to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I owe you no explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is as beautiful\nas a Bodhisattva.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If she were to marry into\nthe Hojo {\i1}family....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,all would be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome {\i1}Hojo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That has such a nice ring to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0} I was {\i1}just....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:42.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:45.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-You're....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're from a nearby village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time, it's their ancestors?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing\nat this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were picking firewood\nfor tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and we sensed your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:05.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You became lost in the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us take you to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really? That would be\na great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But could it be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me borrow this\nfor a second, Hojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought the Demon Ninja\nhad disguised themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I guess I'm being\ntoo suspicious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Inuyasha, a half-demon,\nwas nearly overcome{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the power of the aura\nof the blade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But these girls seem\nto be fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:36.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then... I'll carry you\nto the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll carry your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0} No!\NThis is very valuable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Ninja technique,\NDarkness Puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this technique, the puppets\nwon't be affected by the aura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and they'll be able to\nsteal the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I almost had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:58.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I mean, he was about to\nhand it over to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I keep telling you to cut\nout that act!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have lots of chances left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll catch them off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then we'll steal the Ken blade\nand tear those two apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, how scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can I concentrate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:21.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err.... No....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0} May I ask what kind\nof relationship you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We really don't have\na relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:28.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:31.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You make such a nice couple,\NI thought you were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really? We look good together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome and {\i1}Akitoki....{\i0}\nyou make a wonderful couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, put me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got carried away {\i1}there....{\i0}\NPlease don't get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:55.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you know our names?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's your fault for acting weird\nand making me lose my concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! They're such a bother!\NLet's kill them and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our target is the Ken blade,\nthat's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those are puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why the aura of the blade\ndidn't affect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:26.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:34.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo! Take the Ken blade\nand run to Furai Shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:42.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot leave you by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:52.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:34.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Haven't you figured it out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the power you throw\nat me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:39.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is being absorbed by the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:18.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:22.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This aura is from Hoshiyomi's\NKon blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:25.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Hoshiyomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:29.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we captured the girl, Kagome,\nwho was with that group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:41.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're okay!\NWhere's Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:42.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome {\i1}was....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:44.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome {\i1}was....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:46.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:51.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:53.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:58.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to protect the Ken blade\neven if it means this woman's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:01.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:49.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want to save this woman,\ncome to Furai Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:52.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And make sure you don't\nforget the Ken blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:53.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:56.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Kagome got involved\nin all {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That she fell into\NHoshiyomi's hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:24:02.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't have time for that now!\NWe must save Kagome from that demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.34,0:24:03.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:05.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga still hasn't transformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:09.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Great Duel at Shoun Falls!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:11.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as we have spirit,\nwe can do anything!
